Welcome to asciitron!

This game is related to the movie Tron from 1982.

It supports multiplayer gaming over network; start the server like this:

    python asciitron.py serve X

with X defines how many people will play the game. The server will wait
until all players are connected.

The client is started like this:

    python asciitron.py connect localhost X

with X defines your unique player ID. The ID must be a digit between 1 and 9.

Have fun!
